Constructs a new boxed slice with uninitialized contents.

# Examples

```
let mut values = Box::<[u32]>::new_uninit_slice(3);
// Deferred initialization:
values[0].write(1);
values[1].write(2);
values[2].write(3);
let values = unsafe { values.assume_init() };

assert_eq!(*values, [1, 2, 3])
```
